Emalunga ePhalamende aseWales, esaba kubukeka njengebantfu labatsandvwa ngulabo labahlala nabo emakhaya.
Emalunga lahlukahlukene ePhalamende akhatsatekile ngalolushintjo lolwentiwe kutsi esikhundleni sawo sekuba ngemalunga ePhalamende (AMs) abe ngemalunga ePhalamende (Member of the Welsh Parliament - MWPs).
Loku bekubangelwa kutsi bekunetinhlelo tekutsi ligama lesigodzi liguculwe libe yi-Welsh Parliament.
Emalunga ePhalamende kuto tonkhe tinhlangotsi atimisele kutsi loku kutawenta bantfu bahleke.
Lenye yeMalunga ePhalamende yeLebhu yaseNingizimu Afrika, iLabour Party, itsi bantfu bayo bakhatsatekile ngekutsi leligama litawuhlangana ne-TWP kanye ne-PWP.
Kulabo labangekho eWales, twp isho kutsi "silima" bese pwp kusho kutsi "silikati".
Lilunga lePhalamende lelibitwa ngekutsi yi-Fledend Camry latsi onkhe emalunga aleliPhalamende bekangakatfokoti ngalomsebenti futsi bekaniketwe letinye tindlela.
Lilunga lelicembu le Welsh Conservative Party litsi emalunga alo avulekile kutsi asho tintfo letifana neligama, kepha waphawula kutsi leligama lelitsi MWP (lokutsi lichaza lilunga lePhalamende le Welsh) livakala lifana nalelitsi Muppet.
Ngaloku, le w Welsh ibhalwe ngendlela lefanako naleyo ye u siNgisi, nge-Yuksheshian.
Likomidi lelikhetfwe liSekela laMengameli, lelisaphenya ngekuguculwa kwemagama, litsi: "Sincumo sekugcina macondzana nemagama lachaza imisebenti yemalunga eliSekela laMengameli, siyintfo lesitsatfwa ngemalunga eliSekela laMengameli".
I-Welsh Government Act 2017 inika indlu yesishayamtsetfo emandla ekugucula ligama layo.
Ngenyanga yeNyoni, lelikomidi lakhipha imiphumela yekubonisana kwemmango ngetiphakamiso, lapho khona kwavetwa khona kwesekelwa lokukhulu kwekugucula ligama leSigungu saVelonkhe kutsi libe yiPhalamende yase Welsh.
Mayelana nelibito lemsebenti weMalunga ePhalamende (AMs), lelikomidi laphakamisa kutsi kube 'Malunga ePhalamende aseNingizimu Afrika' nobe ema-WMPs, kepha i-MWP yatfola lusito lolukhulu ekubonisaneni nemphakatsi.
Emalunga esishayamtsetfo ahlele letinye tindlela, kepha kulwa nekutfola kuvumelana kungaletsa tinkinga letikhulu kuSihlalo weLikomidi, Ellen Jones, lofanele kutsi alethe luhlaka lwemitsetfo lemayelana nalolushintjo kumaviki ladvute.
Umtsetfo wekususa usho letinye tingucuko endleleni yekusebenta kweSigungu, kufaka ekhatsi imitsetfo yekukhishwa kweMengameli kanye nesakhiwo seluhlelo lwemaKomiti.
Kuvota kwemalunga ePhalamende ngulapho titfunywa tibekwa khona uma kusaphenywa ngetindzaba temtsetfo.
