Ngekusho kwaMnumzane Adams, bantfu bakulendzawo bebakhumbula kutsi bekunemabhari nemasontfo edvute nalapho kuhlala khona bantfu.
"Manje kute emabhilidi nobe emasontfo".
Watsi kunengcondvo yekuncipha kwaBari.
"Imphilo yebantfu lamuhla yehlukile".
