Mayelana nemasontfo, ukhatsatekile ngekutsi imali letfolakala ngekutsengisa timphahla angeke isebente sikhatsi lesidze njengobe baholi bemasontfo bacabanga, futsi kutawudzingeka kutsi bavele baphindze babuyele endzaweni yabo".
Watsi emasontfo atawutsatfwa njengetindlu letinebantfu labahlala etindzaweni letingafani netemvelo, kute kulondvolotwe imvelo.
"Bantfu labanyenti labatawutsenga tindlu kuleto takhiwo batawuba ngulabamhlophe", kusho yena, "lokungahle kwente emasontfo avale, ngobe bantfu labanyenti labatawutsenga letindlu angeke babe ngemalunga aleto tinkholo".
Lamasontfo lamabili akhiwa ngemasontfo lamhlophe langasese-Harlem ngaphambi kwekutsi kube yindzawo lenemuntfu lomnyama. Lelisontfo le Metropolitan Community Church ngemnyaka wa 1870, ne St. Martin's 10 ngeminyaka lelandzelako.
