Ummango webantfu labamnyama lebebakhonta kulendzawo, sebatfole sikhundla sekuba bakhiciti.
St. Martin's Church yatfunywa licembu lebantfu labamnyama lebebaholwa ngu-Father John Howard Johnson, lowahola umbhikisho webatsengisi lebebakhona ku-125 Street, lokuyindzawo yekutsengisela etinkhundleni eHarlem, lebebaphika kucashwa noma kukhutsatelwa bantfu labamnyama.
Umlilo wanga-1939 wabhidlita kakhulu lesakhiwo, kodvwa njengencenye yeluhlelo lwekwakha kabusha, emakholwa ngaphansi kwaMfundisi Johnson, acela kutsi kwakhiwe i-Crown Bells.
Umfundisi David Johnson, indvodzana yaJohnson lowatalwa nguye futsi lowaba yindlalifa yelibandla le St. Martin, ngekutigcabha wabita lelicembu ngekutsi "Tibondza Teliphupho".
