Umfana loneminyaka lelishumi nakutsatfu walunywa nguhlamvu lolwabulala umfana lowabese uyatikhipha emantini ayofuna emalobster eCalifornia ngelilanga lekucala lemkhicito wawo, kusho tiphatsimandla.
