Nguloko lokwentiwa bantfu!
Hamli watsi nakafika kulomfana wabona kutsi lonkhe litsambo lakhe liwile.
"Ngamemeta bonkhe bantfu kutsi baphume emantini, 'kunekhahlamba emantini!' " kwengeta Hamel.
