Kute lowatiko kutsi ngukuphi kuloluhlobo lwesihlahla semfishi lesasihlasela lomfana.
Umphatsi wetinhlanti Larry Giles ukhulume emhlanganweni wetintsatseli kutsi lemoshaka ibonwe endzaweni emavikini lambalwa lalandzela, kepha kutfolwe kutsi ayiphili.
Giles uchubeka atsi lesidvumbu sinetimphawu letibuhlungu emtimbeni waso.
Baphatsi bemaphoyisa bavale umgwaco losuka ePonto Beach, eKesblade, uye eSwami Beach, eSinitas, emahora langu-48 ngelilanga, bentela kuhlolisisa kanye nekuphepha.
