Lenye indvodza lengisebenta nayo ePhalamende, Govan Ryan, nayo yatfola lomusa lofanako ngobe yakhutsata kakhulu kuphikisana nemaJuda.
Mine, sincumo sekungigcoba, sangihlupha ngekungavumelani kwami naJeremy Corbin.
Ngekubaluleka kwekuhlela ngekwetemnotfo lokunemsebenti, kuvikeleka kwesive, iEurope - ngekuhlekisa lokukhulu, tindzaba letifanako naleto Jeremy labengavumelani ngato nebaholi belicembu leliphelile.
Umhlangano welicembu lelisebenta ngeMgcibelo weLwesihlanu watsi "sifuna lomhlangano ube ngulophumelelisako".
Iminyaka lesiphohlongo lengayihlala njengelunga lePhalamende lelisuka e-Labour, imihlangano ye-General Committee ngeLesihlanu ebusuku beyifana nalena.
Kodvwa-ke lamuhla, loku akusiko lokwente imihlangano leminyenti yalelive ibe ncono, futsi nesetsembiso sepolitiki lenemusa neluvelo sesiphelelwe sikhatsi, nangabe nje vele sesike sacala.
Kuyabonakala kutsi licembu lebasebenti alitibekeleli imibono leyehlukene, futsi imibono leyehlukene yehlukaniswa ngekuya ngekutsi ngabe lemukelekile yini kulicembu lelisetulu.
Loku kwacala ngekushesha ngemuva kwekuba Jeremy akhetfwe njengaSihlalo welicembu, lapho bantfu lebengicabanga kutsi sinebuhlobo lobuhlangene nabo kutembusave, bacala kumcela kutsi ente tintfo lebengingeke ngivumelane naye kuto, kungaba mayelana nekuvikeleka kwesive noma mayelana nekuhleleka kwemakethe yaseYurophu.
Ngaso sonkhe sikhatsi nangikhuluma embikwebantfu - futsi akusho lutfo kutsi ngitsini - ngekushesha nje kuvela umsindvo wekutsi angikhulumi kahle etindzaweni tekuchumana te-social media, ngiva kungatsi kunekugceka, ngisola temibono ye-centre, futsi ngitsi angifaneleki kuba se-Labour.
Akusiko nje kutsi ngiyo lehlose loku.
Ecinisweni, ngiyati kutsi nginenhlanhla kunebangani bami labanyenti, ngobe imibono lecondziswe kimi ivamise kuba ngeyembusave.
