Lesinye setintfo letingajabulisi kakhulu ngalesi sikhatsi setembusave yindlela lizinga lekuhlukunyetwa lebeselisolo liyincenye yekuphila.
Jeremy Corbyn kuleliviki leliphelile watsi licembu letisebenti kumele lifundzise lisiko lekubeketelela.
Liciniso likutsi sesisesimeni lesifanako sekuba nelubandlululo, futsi njalo nakushaywa umtsetfo we-AI-Amnesty nobe kuguculwa kwemitsetfo yelubandlululo, lelicembu liba sesimeni lesibi kakhulu.
Kuleminyaka lemibili lendlulile, bantfu labanyenti bangikhuta ngekutsi ngingachubeki nekukhuluma, bese ngiyahamba.
