Angizange ngicale kufihla imibono yami yetepolitiki, ngisho nangemnyaka lophelile.
Kute umuntfu e-East Nottingham lobekacabanga kutsi nginemibono lephambene neyabohulumende.
Kulabo labaletsa sincumo ngaLesihlanu, konkhe lengikushoko kutsi ngalesikhatsi lelive lisondzela ekushoneni kweBrexit lokutawutsikameta imindeni, emabhizinisi kanye nemisebenti yemphakatsi, angicondze kutsi kungani ngitsandza kusebentisa sikhatsi sami kanye nemandla ami ekutsembekeni ku-Labour leader.
Kepha-ke, umlayeto wami longaniketwa wona, hhayi ku-Momentum Movement eNottingham, kepha kulabo labangikhetsele bona, nobe ngabe bangemalunga e-Labour Party nobe cha: Ngitfokotela kukhonta nine futsi ngetsembisa kutsi kute linani lelisemkhatsini wekwesabisa nobe kutfola tinzuzo tepolitiki letingangiyekisa ekwenteni loko lengikukholelwa kutsi kunetintfo letitawunisita kakhulu.
