Takhiwo temphakatsi tivetwe ngemibala leyehlukile.
Tikhungo temabutfo emikhumbi kusuka eTiticca kuya eAmazon tinemagama latsi: "Lwandle ngeletfu ngekwemtsetfo.
Kungumsebenti wetfu kutsi simcele kutsi aphindze abuye".
Kuyo yonkhe iBolivia lengenandlela yekungena elwandle, kukhunjulwa kwelugwini lolulahlekele ngenca yekungenela kwebantfu baseChile lokwabhebhetselwa ingati yabo ngesikhatsi semzabalazo welitulu lesi-19 wemitfombolusito, kusekhona - kanjalo nesifiso sekuphindze sihambe ngemkhumbi siye ePacific.
Letetsembiso kungenteka betisolo tifezeka kulesikhatsi lesidze, njengobe i-Bolivia ilindzele sincumo lesitawentiwa yiNkantolo Yemave Emhlaba nga-October 1, ngemuva kweminyaka lesihlanu yemkhandlu.
"Bolivia unemandla, umoya wekubumbana kanye nekuthula, futsi-ke ubuke phambili ngekutimisela lokuhle", kwasho Roberto Calzdalilla, ummeli waseBolivia.
