Esikhundleni sekwenta lelicala la Bolivia lichubeke, leminyaka lemine leyendlulile yente kwaba ncono.
"Lendzaba yekufinyelela elwandle seyivele isunguliwe nguhulumende nyalo eBolivia", kusho Zaratata.
