John Edward: Lwati lwetilwimi lubalulekile ekwakheni sakhamuti salelive
Tikolwa letitimele taseScotland tibambe lirekhodi lelisetulu lemfundvo, lokuchubekela embili nga-2018 nalokunye kuhlangana kwemiphumela lemihle kakhulu yekuhlola, lokuchutjwa kuphumelela kwemuntfu ngamunye kanye nekwelicembu kutemidlalo, tebuciko, umculo kanye naletinye tintfo letibalulekile emphakatsini.
Njengoba tikhashane ngetulu kwe 30,000 bafundzi eScotland, letikolwa, letimele i Scottish Council of Independent Schools (SCIS), tifuna kuniketa lizinga lelisetulu lekufundzisa bafundzi kanye nebatali.
Tikolwa letizimele tifuna kulungiselela bafundzi bato kutsi batfole imfundvo lephakeme, batfole nemisebenti labangayenta, futsi babe takhamuti temhlaba wonkhe.
Njengemkhakha wemfundvo lowati kuklama nekusebentisa tifundvo letetayelekile, siyatfola kutsi tilwimi talamuhla tichubeka nekutfola kutsandvwa njengesifundvo lesifunwako etikolweni.
Nelson Mandela watsi, "Uma ukhuluma nemuntfu ngelulwimi lalucondzako, uyakucondza loko".
"Nawukhuluma nemuntfu ngelulwimi lwakhe, loko kuyamtsintsa inhlitiyo yakhe".
Loku kusikhumbuta lokukhulu kutsi singeke sisebentise lulwimi lwesiNgisi kuphela nasita kwakha budlelwane nekwetsembana nebantfu bakulamanye emave.
Ngekuya ngekubuka loku lokwentiwe ekuhloleni kwaleminyaka lendlulile, tilwimi tibonakala tihola kakhulu etikolweni letifundziswa ngekutimela.
Emaphesenti langu-68 ebafundzi labafundza tilwimi letinye batfole emamaki laphakeme.
Emaphesenti langu-72 ebantfwana bazuza ema-A laphakeme ngesiMandarin, loku kufaka ekhatsi emaphesenti langu-72 lafundza siJalimane, emaphesenti langu-69 lafundza siFulentji, kanye nemaphesenti langu-63 lafundza siSpanish.
Lemininingwane ikhombisa kutsi tikolo letitimele eScotland tisekela kukhuluma tilwimi letingetiwe njengelwati lolubalulekile lolutodzinga kutfutfwa bantfwana kanye nebantfwana labaseminyakeni yekutfomba.
Nyalo tilimi setitsatfwa njengaletifundvwa esikolweni njengaletifundvwa etikolweni tekusebenta ngetandla kanye nakuletinye tikhungo.
Luhlolo lwanga-2014 lolwentiwa yiBritish Council for Employment and Skills lwatfola kutsi 17% wabasebenti bakhomba kutsi kuba bete lwati lwemsebenti lolungilo, ngenca yekungabi nelwati lwekukhuluma lulwimi.
Ngaloko, ngekukhula, likhono lekufundza tilwimi letinsha liba sidzingo lesibalulekile kute kulungiselelwe bafundzi imisebenti yabo yelikusasa.
Ngenca yekukhula kwetidzingo telulwimi ematfuba emisebenti esikhatsini lesitako, lamakhono ayadzingeka kulomhlaba lotfutfuke ngalokwengetekile.
Kunobe ngumuphi umsebenti umuntfu langakhetsa kuwutsatsa, kufundza lulwimi lwesibili kutawumenta abe nelikhono lelihle lelimcoka ekuphileni kwakhe.
Kuba nelikhono lekuchumana ngco nebantfu labasuka kulamanye emave ngekwe-othomati kukwenta ube nemandla kunalabanye.
Ngekusho kweluhlolo lwe-YouGov lolwentiwe ku-4,000 yebantfu labadzala base-UK nga-2013, emaphesenti langu-75 abengakhoni kukhuluma lulwimi lwangaphandle ngelizinga lelifanele lekuchumana, kantsi siFulentji bekunguleso kuphela lesasinetinombolo letimbili telulwimi, emaphesenti la-15.
Kungako kubalulekile kutsi sibeke imali kufundzisa bantfwana betfu tilwimi.
Kwati tilwimi letinyenti, ikakhulukati letiphuma emaveni lasatfutfuka, kungenta bantfwana babe nelitfuba lelihle lekutfola umsebenti lonetindzaba letimnandzi.
Kulesinye simo, tikolwa tiyehluka ngetilwimi letisetjentiswa khona.
Letinye tifundvo titawubhekisa kakhulu kulokusha kwetilwimi, letinye tifundziswe etilwimini letibukeka tibalulekile e-UK ngeminyaka yabo-1920 kuya ku-2021, njengesiMandarin nesiJapane.
Nobe ngabe umntfwana utsandzani, kutawuba netilwimi letehlukene langakhetsa kuto etikolweni letizimele, letinebafundzisi labati kakhulu.
Tikolwa taseScotland letizimele tibophelele ekuhlinzekeni ngesimondzawo sekufundza lesilungiselela bantfwana kanye nekubaniketa emakhono ladzingekako kute baphumelele, esikhatsini lesitako.
Angeke kuphikwe kutsi namuhla, esimeni sebhizinisi lelisheshe lahlangana, tilwimi tisolo tibalulekile kulikusasa lalelive, ngako-ke loku kufanele kuhlangabetane nemfundvo.
Kuliciniso kutsi tilwimi tesimanje tibitwa ngekutsi "tindlela tekuchumana temave emhlaba".
Tikolwa letitimele titawuchubeka nekuniketa lokulizinga lekutikhetsela, kwehlukahlukana kanye nekuphumelela kubantfwana baseScotland.
