HIV/AIDS: E-China ibika kwenyuka lokungu-14% kwebantfu labasha labangenwa nguleligciwane
I-China imemetele kwenyuka kwa 14% yelinani lebantfu labaphila ne HIV/AIDS.
Bantfu labangu-820 000 babhekene nalesifo, kusho tiphatsimandla tetemphilo.
Emkhatsini wa-2018, bekunebantfu labangu-40 000 lebebangenwe sifo se-TB.
Emazinga lamanyenti lamasha atfolakala ngekulala nalabanye bantfu, lokungumkhuba lomusha.
Nyalo i-HIV seyisakateke ngekushesha etindzaweni letitsite e-China ngenca yekumpontshelwa ingati lengcolile.
Kodvwa linani lebantfu labatsatseka ngalesifo se-HIV linciphile laba ngu-zero, ngekusho kwebasebenti betemphilo base-China labamemetela lomhlangano wesigodzi sase-Yunnan.
Kodvwa, ngemnyaka ngamunye, linani lebantfu labaphila ne-HIV/AIDS eChina likhule nga-100 000.
Kutseleleka nge-HIV ngekuya ecasini kuyinkinga lematima kubantfu labashadile e-China.
Bantfu labatsandzana ngekwelicasi abakapheleliswa emtsetfweni eChina nga-1997, kepha kukhulunywa ngekutsi kubandlululwa kwebantfu labatsandzanako kuyachubeka.
Ngenca yemasiko alomhlaba lasendzaweni, tifundvo titfole kutsi 70% kuya ku 90% wemadvodza lalala nalamanye emadvodza agcina sekashade nalabafati.
Tinyenti tifo letitfolakala kubantfu lababanjwe ngemagciwane letibangelwa kungatisebentisi kahle tindlela tekutivikela.
