Yini i-World Citizens' Festival futsi ngabe yente lokutsite kute kuncishiswe buphuya?
NgeliSontfo, iNew York beyibukete iWorld Citizens Festival, umcimbi wemculo wemnyaka wonkhe loneluhlu loluhle lwetinkanyezi letitako kanye nemgomo lomkhulu wekucedza buphuya emhlabeni.
Lomkhosi wemave emhlaba, nyalo sewutakwentiwa iminyaka lesikhombisa, utawuletsa tinkhulungwane tebantfu ebaleni lelikhulu le-Central Park hhayi nje kuphela kute tijabulele imibukiso lefana naGrant Jackson, Cardi B na Sean Mendes, kodvwa kute ticaphele umgomo wawo - kucedza umtselo ngalokuphelele nga-2030.
I-World Citizens' Festival leyacala nga 2012 ilandzelwa yi-Global Poverty Project, licembu lemasiko lahlukene lelitsemba kucedza buphuya ngekukhulisa linani lebantfu labalwe nabo.
Kute utfole likhadi lekuhamba mahhala lelihamba embili (ngaphandle uma ngabe utikhetsela kukhokhela umshwalensi we-VIP), bantfu labatawube bakhona kulomcimbi kumele bacedzele luhlelo lwemisebenti, nobe ?imisebenti? lefana nekuvolontiya, kutfumela umlayeto nge-email kumholi wemhlaba, kubita nobe letinye tindlela letitsite tekusita ekwandziseni lwati ngenhloso yekucedza buphuya.
Kodvwa, i-Festival yaba yimphumelelo lenjani, njengobe bekusele nje iminyaka lelishumi nakubili kutsi ifinyelele lapho beyifuna kuya khona?
Ngabe lomcondvo wekuniketa bantfu emathikithi amahhala ekonsathi uyindlela yekubancenga kutsi bafune kwenta lokutsite, nobe ngulenye indlela yekutsi ?klikativism? bantfu labativa shengatsi banemandla ngekusayina i-tweet nobe ngemlayeto we-twitter?
Kusukela nga-2011, i-WCC itsi inikete ngetulu kwetigidzi leti-19 tetento temalunga ayo, ngekucinisekisa tinhloso letehlukene.
Utsi lemisebenti isitile kucinisa baholi bemhlaba ngekumemetela kutibophetela netinchubomgomo letitawuholela etinkingeni letingetulu kwetigidzigidzi letingu-R37 letitawuchuba timphilo tebantfu labangetulu kwetigidzigidzi letimbili nemakhulu lamabili nemashumi lasihlanu nga-2030.
Ekucaleni kwemnyaka wa 2018, lelicembu labalabo 390 labalandzele imiculu yabo, lokungaba ngunyalo, tigidzigidzi letilishumi temadola lasevele atfoliwe nobe lacalwe ngekuhambisa nobe kukhulisa imali.
Lelicembu lilingisa kutsi imali leyakhelwe ngaphambilini seyitfole umtselela locondzile kubantfu labalinganiselwa kutigidzi letingu-649 mhlabawonkhe.
Tikhungo letimbalwa tifaka ekhatsi iThe Power of Nutrition, inhlanganisela yaseNgilandi yebasomabhizinisi kanye nebatsengisi labatimisele kusita bantfwana kutsi bakhule baphelele, nekutfola tigidzi temadola letingu-35 kutsi basite kucedza kungadli kahle eNingizimu Afrika, ngemuva kwekutfola ema-tweets langetulu kwa-4 700 lavela kulabantfu labavela emaveni emhlaba.
Ngekusekelwa nguhulumende wase UK, banikeli, bohulumende betive kanye netakhamiti temhlaba wonkhe njengani, singenta bulungiswa bemphakatsi mayelana nekudla lokungekho ezingeni lemphilo, kusho Umlamuli weMandla ekuDla, Tracey Ullman, etinkhulumeni ngesikhatsi semcimbi lophilako eLondon ngeNdlovana 2018.
