Nanobe kuliciniso kutsi bohulumende bangaphandle bangakhangisa kute batfutfukise kutsengiselana, iBeijing ne Washington nyalo sebatimphini tekulwa timphi tekutsengiselana lapho khona onkhe emave akhuphula futsi ahlanganise lizinga lemitselo yetimphahla temikhicito lechamuka emaveni akubo.
I-China yenyuse umtsetfo wekukhokhela intsela kulesinye sikhatsi semphi yekuhweba, lemisho yekukhokhela imphahla kumave lafana ne-Iowa leyesekela i-Republican Party ya-Trump, kusho bocwepheshe baseMelika nebase-China.
Terry Bernstad, lobekasolo angumbonisi waseMelika eChina, lobekabuye abe ngundvunankhulu eIowa iminyaka leminyenti, futsi lobekangumtsengisi lomkhulu wetintfo tekulima eChina, utsi Beijing ihlabe bantfu eMelika labasebenta, balimi kanye nebemabhizinisi.
I-China, wabhala Bernstad esihlokweni lesitsite ku-Daily Herald, "isekela tento tebudlova ngekukhangisa etincwadzini tetfu letikhululekile".
Ngekwenta lomkhankhaso, hulumende waseChina usebentisa lisiko laseMelika lekukhuluma ngekukhululeka kanye nekwenta umsebenti wekutfutfukisa tindzaba, ngekubeka sikhangisi lesikhokhelwako e-Da Moyne Registry, kusho Bernstad.
"Ngenca yaloko, etincenyeni temaphephandzaba letisemgwacweni eBeijing, utawutfola timphandze letimbalwa futsi ngeke utfole ngisho nalinye livi lelicinisekisiwe leliveta imibono leyehlukene bantfu baseShayina labangase babe nayo mayelana nendlela leyesabekako yetemnotfo, njengobe betindzaba tabo batiwa kakhulu liCembu leKhomanisi laseShayina", wabhala njalo.
Waphindze wengeta kutsi: "Lelinye liphephandzaba lelibalulekile eChina liyekele kuchaza kutsi litawushicilela yini lesihloko, nanobe angakacacisi kutsi nguyiphi lephephandzaba".
