Umsunguli we-World Wide Web uhlela kucala i-Internet lensha kuze adlule i-Google ne-Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, umsunguli we-Internet, wacala inkampani lencane lefuna kucudzelana ne-Facebook, Amazon kanye ne-Google.
Inrupt, umklamo wekugcina walendvodza leyaba ngumuntfu lomkhulu kutekutsengisa, yintfo leyakha iSolid, i-platform yemitfombo levulekile ye-Berners-Lee.
I-Solid Platform ivumela basebentisi bakhetse kutsi bangayigcina kuphi imininingwane yabo nekutsi bobani labatfola kufinyelela kuloluhlobo lwe-data.
Kucocisana lokucondzile ne Fast Company, Berners-Lee wahleka ngekutsi inhloso ye Inrupt kutsi "kulawula umhlaba".
"Kufanele sikwente nyalo".
Lesi sikhatsi semlandvo.
Le-app isebentisa buchwepheshe be-Solid kuvumela bantfu kutsi bakhe i-database yabo ye-inthanethi nobe i-POD.
Loluhla lungafaka ekhatsi luhlu lwebangani, luhlu lwekusebenta, luhlu lwekusebenta, libhuku lemculo kanye naletinye tintfo letitsite letitsite letisebentako.
Asewucabange kutsi i-Google Drive, i-Microsoft Outlook, i-Slack kanye ne-Spotify konkhe kutfolakala kusiphequluli sinye ngesikhatsi sinye.
Lokwenta i-e-database ibe ngulenye indlela yekuyichumana kutsi umuntfu loyisebentisako nguye yedvwa loncuma kutsi ngubani longayichumana nekutsi ngutiphi tinhlobo telwati letingachumana naye.
Inhlangano ibita loku "kutiphatsa ngekwe-data".
Ngekusho kwaJohn Bruce, umphatsi we-Inrupt, inhloso kutsi i-Inrupt itfole imitfombo, inchubo kanye nemakhono lafanele ekusiteni i-Solid kutsi isebente kahle.
Kwanyalo lelibhizinisi lifaka ekhatsi iBerners-Lee, iBruce, luhlelo lwekuvikela lolwatfolwa yi-IBM, licembu lelakhiwa bacambi labacashiwe labasebenta kulomsebenti, kanye nemalunga lavolontiya ngekusebentisa ikhodi.
Kusukela kuleliviki, batfwebuli betintfo tebucwepheshe mhlabawonkhe batawukwati kwakha tinhlelo letisetjentiswako ngekusebentisa emathuluzi latfolakala ku-inrupt.com.
Berners-Lee utsi yena nelicembu lakhe abakacoci naFacebook kanye naGoogle mayelana nekutsi bangabhalisa yini nobe bangabhalisi yini ngalokunye lokungagucula luhlelo lwabo lwebhizinisi ngalokuphelele.
Asikaceli imvume yabo.
Ku-post lephuma ku-Medium ngeMgcibelo, Berners-Lee wabhala kutsi umsebenti we-Inrupt  kutsi kunikete emandla ekuhweba kanye nesakhiwo semvelo kusita kuvikela bucotfo kanye nekuphumelela kwalendlela lensha ye-network leyakhiwe e-Solid.
Nga 1994, Berners-Lee wacala wacinisa i-Internet ngekwakha inhlangano leyenta i-Internet, i-W3C, leyakhiwa yi-MIT.
Kuletinyanga letimbalwa letengcile, Berners-Lee bekangilo livi leliphetse etinkhulumeni tekutsi i-Net neutrality ingatsatsi lichaza.
Kantsi nangesikhatsi sekusungulwa kwe Inrupt, Berners-Lee utawuchubeka ngekusebenta njengasungameli kanye nemcondzisi we W3C, iWeb Foundation, kanye ne-Open Data Institute.
"Nginelitsemba lelikhulu ngemnyaka lotako we-Internet", kwengeta Berners-Lee.
