Brexit: I-UK iyalila ngekulahlekelwa bakhiciti bemoto
I-United Kingdom itawutivela buhlungu kakhulu nangabe ilahlekelwa sikhundla sayo sekuba ngumkhiphi lomkhulu wetimoto emhlabeni wonkhe ngemuva kwe-Brexit, kusho iNdvuna yelitiko letemabhizinisi, Greg Clarke.
Wengeta ngekutsi, i-BBC Begazzini ya-Toyota eBritain, lapho atsi khona uma i-Britain ishiya i-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano itawuyekela kukhicita kwesikhashana eBurneston, eceleni kwe-Derby, bekukuhlekisa kakhulu.
"Sidzinga sivumelwano", kwasho Clark.
Umkhicito wetimoto waseJapan utsi kubambeleleka kwemincele uma ngabe iBrexit ingentiwe kutawukhokhela emisebenti.
Luphiko lwaseBurneston - lolukhicita i-Auris ne-Aventis ye-Toyota - lwakhicita timoto leticishe tibe ngu-150 000 ngemnyaka lophelile kantsi 90% yato yayikhicitelwa emaveni lasemkhatsini e-EU.
"Ngekubona kwami, uma iBritish ikhipha i-EU ngaphandle kwensimbi yekusebenta ekupheleni kwaMashi, sitawubona kuphela kwekukhicita kwemboni yetfu", kusho Marvin Cook, umcondzisi weToyota eBurneston.
Labanye bakhiciti betimoto baseBrithani bakhuluma ngekukhatsateka ngekutsi kungabi nesivumelwano se-EU kutawuba namuphi umtselela ekutsengisweni kwetimoto e-EU, kufaka ekhatsi i-Honda, i-BMW, i-Victoria Land Rover.
Sibonelo, inkampani ye-BMW itsi itawuvala imboni yayo ye-LGBT e-Oxford, e-England, inyanga ngemuva kwe-Brexit.
Lokubaluleke kakhulu nguloko lokutsi bakhiciti betimoto babita ?ngemisebenti yekuhambisa tintfo? uma ngabe kungekho kuvunyelwana.
Umkhakha wekukhicita weToyota usebenta ngetikhatsi leticondzile, ngetincenye letifika njalo ngemizuzu lengemashumi lasikhombisa nesikhombisa, kusuka kubaphakeli baseBrithani kanye ne-EU, kute bakhicite timoto ngendlela lekhishiwe.
Uma iNgilandi ishiya i-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano nga-March 29, kutawuba nekuhlukunyetwa kwemincele, futsi labateliti betemisebenti batsi kutawuholela ekubambeni kanye nasekuswebeni tintfo.
I-Toyota angeke ikhone kubamba emalungiselelo ladzinga lilanga linye kuphela esitifikeni se-Derbyshire, kusho inkampani, ngako-ke umkhicito utawuyekelwa.
Clark utsi luhlelo lwaTheresa May lwe "Crucifiers", loluhlela budlelwane beBrithani ne EU, lwahlelwa kahle kute kuvinjelwe lokuhlolwa emingceleni.
"Kufanele sifinyelele esivumelwaneni. Sifuna kufinyelela esivumelwaneni lesikahle kakhulu, njengobe ngishito, hhayi nje kuphela kutsi sijabulele imphumelelo yanyalo, kodvwa kutsi sibambe lomatfuba", washo njalo ku Today ku BBC Radio 4.
"Bufakazi lobubonakalako lobubekwe nguToyota kanye nalabanye bakhiciti betimoto kutsi kuchuba luhlelo lwemkhicito loluphumelele, lesesikadze sinalo, kubaluleke kakhulu".
I-Toyota ayizange isho kutsi loku kucedvwa kwekukhicita kutawuhlala sikhatsi lesingakanani, kepha ngekuhamba kwesikhatsi, icwayise ngekutsi kukhuphuka kwetindleko kutawulimata kuchudzelana kwe-factory futsi ekugcineni kubangele kucedvwa kwemisebenti.
Peter Covalarris, lobekasebente eBarnaston iminyaka lengemashumi lamabili nakune, futsi lobekabuye abe ngumengameli weLicembu lalabantfu labamunye kulefemu, utsi emalunga elicembu aya ngekuba nekukhatsateka lokukhulu: "Ngekubona kwami, uma lemisebenti incipha, angeke iphindze ivuselelwe".
Sikhulumi sahulumende satsi: "Sente luhlelo lolucondzile nalolunengcondvo lwebudlelwane betfu ne-European Union esikhatsini lesitako".
Umhlangano waTrump naRosenstein ungahlehliswa futsi, kusho iWhite House
Umhlangano wa Donald Trump naSekela-Mshushisi-Jikelele Rod Rosenstein, lobekahlele kuwuvala, kungenteka uhlehliswe liviki lelisetulu njengobe imphi yelicembu leNkantolo lephakeme, Bert Kavanaugh, ichubeka, kusho iNdlu yeMhlophe ngeLisontfo.
Rosenstein ulawula umsebenti welihhovisi leMmeli loMkhulu Robert Mueller, lophenya ngekuhlanganisa kweRussia elukhetfweni, budlelwane emkhatsini webasiti ba Trump kanye neRussia kanye nekungenelela lokungenteka kwebuphekula kwaMengameli.
Tinkhulumo eWashington betikhuluma ngetinyanga tekutsi ngabe Trump utawucosha umshushisi lowengamele bese ulimata inkhululeko yaMueller.
Ekucaleni kwenyanga, iNew York Times ibike kutsi Rosenstein bekatfola litfuba lekuba nesibambo semsakato kute abhale inkhulumo yaTrump bese aphokophelela kutsi Mengameli asuswe esikhundleni ngeSichibiyelo se-25 semTsetfosisekelo.
Rosenstein wasiphika lesimemetelo.
Kodvwa ngelilanga lelilandzelako wafika eNdlini leNgcwele, futsi kubikwa kutsi bekatawushiya sikhundla sakhe.
Esikhundleni saloko, kwabekwa umhlangano wa-Eva naTrump, lobekafike ngesikhatsi Rosenstein afika emhlanganweni we-United Nations eNew York.
Trump watsi angafuna kumkhipha Rosenstein esikhundleni kodvwa ngalesisikhatsi lomhlangano walungiswa kuze kugwenywe kungcubutana nelicala lekomidi lelisemtsetfweni leSeneti lapho khona kwafakaza Kavanaugh kanye nalomunye walabafati labamsola ngekutiphatsa kabi ngekwelicasi, Dokotela Christine Blaise Ford.
Ngalelolanga, Trump watfumela li-FBI kutsi lihlole emaviki lambalwa emacala labhekiswe kuKavanaugh, waphindze futsi wabeka eceleni kuvotelwa kweSigungu Savelonkhe.
Sarah Sanders, losikhulumi saTrump, uvele ku-Fox News ngeLesihlanu.
Ekuphendvuleni umbuto mayelana nekuhlangana naRosenstein, watsi: "Lusuku alukatiwa, kungenteka kutsi luhlangane lutawubanjwa kuleliviki, ngingabona kutsi lungahlehliswa yini lolunye liviki ngenca yaloko lokwenteka eNkantolo lePhakeme".
Kodvwa sitawucoca, futsi ngiyajabula kukwatisa betindzaba.
Labanye babhali bangabuka lesincumo, batsi Sanders akake abambe inkhulumomphikiswano neNdlu yeLusibalukhulu kusukela ngaSeptemba 10.
Chris Wallace, lobekacondzisa lomcimbi, wabuta kutsi kungani.
Sanders watsi lokungavami kwaletincwadzi bekungasho kutsi bekangemukeleki kutsi babhali bethelevishini babe setikhundleni, watsi: "Ngingeke ngiphike kutsi bayasitfola lesikhundla".
Ngemuva kwaloko, wabuye waveta kutsi kufanele akhulise kuchumana kwakhe nemaphephandzaba.
